def reverse_string(s):
    left, right = 0, len(s) - 1
    while left < right:
        s[left], s[right] = s[right], s[left]
        left += 1
        right -= 1
    return s

if __name__ == '__main__':
    import json
    s = json.loads(input())
    result = reverse_string(s)
    print(json.dumps(result))
